## Getting Started

1. Install dependencies in both server and client folders.

    ```bash
    npm install
    ```

2. Create .env file in server folder

    ```bash
    DB_MONGO_HOST=
    ```

3. Install [MongoDB](https://www.mongodb.com/) on your machine

4. Start the server => from the server folder, run

    ```bash
   npm start
    ```

5. Start the client => from the client folder, run

    ```bash
    npm start
    ```